          keyword research and on-page optimization solely will be not enough to
          reach the targets without optimizing a website's technical
          infrastructure and architecture which also plays a crucial role in
          affecting website visibility and ranking in search engines.
        </span>
        <span>
          My favorite part of coding is that it allows me to constanly challenge
          my self to learn new thing. Building websites from a cool design that
          has been well thought out is a amazing journey where I can apply my
          innovation and new ideas can be implemented with a user-centric
          approach into the visually appealing and intuitive digital
          experiences.
        </span>
      </div>
